title: >-
  Climate modelling comparing volatile anaesthetics and
  total intravenous anaesthesia using FaIR v2.2.4
message: >-
  Software used for the publication: "Global temperature
  effect of general anaesthesia: a climate modelling study
  comparing volatile anaesthetic agents and total
  intravenous anaesthesia (1956–2500)" 
